LICENSE INFORMATION
-------------------

The CFITSIO Perl module is relased under the same terms as Perl itself.
Please see the "README" file in the Perl distribution for more details.

CFITSIO is a library of ANSI C routines for reading and writing FITS
format data files. It is actively mainted by William Pence, and can
be obtained from http://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/fitsio.

